Description: pi-Stomp application — guitar effects pedalboard software
 The pi-Stomp application code, uv-managed venv, and systemd service.
 Installs to /opt/pistomp/pi-stomp/ with a symlink at
 /home/pistomp/pi-stomp for deploy.sh compatibility.
 .
 Ships .git-meta/ (origin URL, branch, built-sha) instead of a .git
 directory. Run util/expand-git.sh on the device to seed a real git repo,
 fetch full history and tags, and enable `git describe --dirty=*`.
